# Pattern Recognition

This directory stores identified patterns from team decisions.

## Files

- `successful-patterns.json` - Patterns with >90% success rate
- `anti-patterns.json` - Patterns with <70% success rate
- `emerging-patterns.json` - New patterns being tracked

## Pattern Structure

```json
{
  "pattern-name": {
    "description": "Pattern description",
    "successRate": 0.95,
    "count": 15,
    "decisions": ["dec-001", "dec-002"],
    "characteristics": [
      "Characteristic 1",
      "Characteristic 2"
    ],
    "recommendation": "When to use this pattern"
  }
}
```
